{"tid":652538,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"全球2億用戶稱「單身」　FB推約會功能助找對象","createTime":"2018-05-04T02:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T05:39:33.000Z","uid":70014,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cd8dfe9d30a857ea87d22254155bc99165d44e28","tid":652538,"uid":70014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T02:12:30.000Z","msg":"全球最大社交網路平台facebook計劃推出配對約會服務，幫助用戶尋找戀愛長期關係。Facebook於美國當地周二(1日)舉行一年一度的開發者大會，facebook行政總裁朱克伯格(Mark Zuckerberg)在會中表示，facebook大約有2億名用戶把感情狀態標記為單身，顯然配對約會服務大有可為。<br />\n<br />\n朱克伯格指，facebook考慮推出配對約會服務超過10年，而此服務現將快推出，預料可提高facebook在年輕用戶群的普及程度，亦可令人們更頻繁訪問該網站。<br />\n<br />\n朱克伯格又指，facebook的配對約會服務將用於尋找及建立長期關係，而非只有約會，亦不會強制用戶使用該服務。對於安全和隱私問題，朱克伯格強調，約會活動不會顯示在facebook的動態消息上，用戶在facebook上的好友亦不會看到用戶在約會平台上的資料，配對的對象也不會是用戶已有的朋友。<br />\n<br />\n(路透社/自由時報)<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180502/s00001/1525231009193?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180502%2Fs00001%2F1525231009193%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=r5NaYUvcD5nygBdEdwe5qrDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=e0a2a6a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180502%2Fs00001%2F1525231009193%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=b2876b26\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180502/s00001/1525231009193?web_push=1</a>"},{"pid":"b111ebcf7493a39b9b87d558ef50071e0a8c0067","tid":652538,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T02:14:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10a0a7a023e4c6b679be8a4960b08510ed4c9558","tid":652538,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T02:15:14.000Z","msg":"又抄"},{"pid":"123f7c42e77748a1bb6cd6d2296b1ae98f937306","tid":652538,"uid":179467,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T02:15:52.000Z","msg":"Facebook正式變Fuckbook <img sr